## 密码朋克 Cypherpunk 💾

本周 [Parity 更换了它们的 GPG Key](https://twitter.com/ParityTech/status/1151563940410908672)，想要了解更多。可以阅读下面的文章。

> There are, as you’re about to see, lots of problems with PGP. Fortunately, if you’re not morbidly curious, there’s a simple meta-problem with it: it was designed in the 1990s, before serious modern cryptography. No competent crypto engineer would design a system that looked like PGP today, nor tolerate most of its defects in any other design.
—— [Latacora, The PGP Problem](https://latacora.micro.blog/2019/07/16/the-pgp-problem.html)


- [《個資風暴：劍橋分析事件》| 正式預告 | Netflix](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qRQEXmg3RaE)



